Package: libmodule-build-pluggable-perl
Version: 0.10-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Debian Perl Group <pkg-perl-maintainers@lists.alioth.debian.org>
Installed-Size: 58
Depends: perl, libclass-accessor-lite-perl, libclass-method-modifiers-perl, libdata-optlist-perl, libmodule-build-perl, libtest-sharedfork-perl
Section: perl
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://metacpan.org/release/Module-Build-Pluggable
Description: plugins for the perl module Module::Build
 Module::Build::Pluggable adds pluggability for Module::Build. You can call
 HOOK_prepare on preparing arguments for Module::Build->new, HOOK_configure
 on configuration step, and HOOK_build on build step.
